      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697407,
      "updated": 1652697407
    },
    {
      "id": "62822b285e90c000009fd1ca",
      "text": "(おのの・たかむら)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697894,
      "updated": 1652697903
    },
    {
      "id": "628229415e90c000009fd1b9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/fc819d8a51b589338ade0fe46759e24f]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697408,
      "updated": 1652697409
    },
    {
      "id": "628229575e90c000009fd1bd",
      "text": " >『孝子の月』（[月岡芳年]『[月百姿]』）両親のために薪を集める小野篁",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697430,
      "updated": 1698377956
    },
    {
      "id": "628229545e90c000009fd1bc",
      "text": " [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/小野篁 小野篁 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697426,
      "updated": 1652697437
    },
    {
      "id": "6282295e5e90c000009fd1be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697437,
      "updated": 1652697438
    },
    {
      "id": "628229605e90c000009fd1bf",
      "text": "[嵯峨天皇]の頃の[公家]・[文人]・[歌人]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697438,
      "updated": 1652697467
    },
    {
      "id": "628229515e90c000009fd1bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697423,
      "updated": 1652697423
    },
    {
      "id": "628229d95e90c000009fd1c2",
      "text": "[隠岐]に流されたことがある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697559,
      "updated": 1652697572
    },
    {
      "id": "6282297e5e90c000009fd1c0",
      "text": " [遣唐副使]に任じられたときに遣唐大使の[藤原常嗣]の行いに抗議して乗船を拒否し",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697468,
      "updated": 1652697731
    },
    {
      "id": "62822a895e90c000009fd1c9",
      "text": "  病気や老母の世話を口実にしたらしい(日本文徳天皇実録に記事があるらしい)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697735,
      "updated": 1652697886
    },
    {
      "id": "62822a855e90c000009fd1c8",
      "text": " [西道謡]という遣唐使を風刺した漢詩を作った",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697731,
      "updated": 1652697731
    },
    {
      "id": "653b31245e90c00000e45f4f",
      "text": " 　そもそも漢詩がすごく上手",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698378019,
      "updated": 1698378045
    },
    {
      "id": "628229ec5e90c000009fd1c3",
      "text": " これが[嵯峨上皇]の怒りに触れて[流罪]になった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697578,
      "updated": 1652697610
    },
    {
      "id": "62822a135e90c000009fd1c4",
      "text": "  数年後に赦免されて帰京した",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697617,
      "updated": 1652697630
    },
    {
      "id": "628229965e90c000009fd1c1",
      "text": " >[思ひきや夷のわかれに衰へて海人の縄たく漁せむとは]〈古今和歌集・雑下・961〉",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697492,
      "updated": 1665843128
    },
    {
      "id": "62822a235e90c000009fd1c5",
      "text": "  思いもよらなんだ、(まさか親しい人たちと別れ、)いなかで落ちぶれ弱りはて、縄を引いて魚をとろうとは…",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697633,
      "updated": 1652697706
    },
    {
      "id": "62822a535e90c000009fd1c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652697681,
      "updated": 1652697681
    },
    {
      "id": "62828763aff09e0000965d8d",
      "text": "脳内で「さんぎのたかむら」と再生されるが、これは役職かな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652721508,
      "updated": 1652721533
    },
    {
      "id": "62828766aff09e0000965d8e",
      "text": " 亡くなる前に[従三位][参議]に叙せられたようですね[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1652721510,
      "updated": 1665894765
    },
    {
      "id": "634b89505e90c0000091da8e",
      "text": "  [日本文徳天皇実録]に記事があるらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1665894736,
      "updated": 1665895039
    },
    {
      "id": "634b8a7f5e90c0000091da8f",
      "text": "   [https://dl.ndl.go.jp/info:ndljp/pid/2563186/19 日本文徳天皇実録 10巻. 4 - 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1665895039,
      "updated": 1665895044
    },
    {
      "id": "634ff7505e90c000006e62a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666185040,
      "updated": 1666185040
    },
    {
      "id": "634ff7865e90c000006e62a4",
      "text": "[書]をよくした人でもある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666185095,
      "updated": 1666185107
    },
    {
      "id": "634ff7925e90c000006e62a6",
      "text": " 後世、江戸時代に「[小野篁歌字尽]」という漢字の教科書も出た",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666185107,
      "updated": 1666185170
    },
    {
      "id": "634ff7d05e90c000006e62a9",
      "text": "  似たような形の漢字を覚えるように工夫してある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666185168,
      "updated": 1666185228
    },
    {
      "id": "634ff7885e90c000006e62a5",
      "text": "   [https://rmda.kulib.kyoto-u.ac.jp/item/rb00009645#?c=0&m=0&s=0&cv=0&r=0&xywh=-1435%2C-184%2C7818%2C3671 小野篁歌字尽 | 京都大学貴重資料デジタルアーカイブ]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666185097,
      "updated": 1666185256
    },
    {
      "id": "634ff81a5e90c000006e62ab",
      "text": "  これが広く使われたのに目をつけた[式亭三馬]は、「[小野ばかむら譃字尽]」という滑稽本を出している(1806)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666185242,
      "updated": 1685758940
    },
    {
      "id": "653b1a215e90c00000ef966a",
      "text": "  　[小野ばかむら譃字尽]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698372129,
      "updated": 1698372178
